Reference-baseline citation
================================================================================

PromptGuard's blog post and methodology compare against the LiteLLM-native
pattern-matching approach described by:

  Rama (Muh. Fani Akbar), "Masking PII Or Sensitive Data Before Sending to
  AI Using LiteLLM," 2026-04-24,
  https://labs.secengai.com/p/masking-pii-or-sensitive-data-before-sending-to-ai-using-litellm

The comparison is conceptual; PromptGuard does not redistribute code or
content from that post.

